<plot>Set in the near future deep within a cosmopolitan financial metropolis, this story follows our heroine on a journey towards her ultimate goal. The audience, innocent to this goal, will travel through an imposing night time cityscape and witness a thriller which leaves them actively questioning whether the actions are materialistic, ethical or whether sexual desire supersedes any corporate responsibility. A timely story in a world of financial turmoil.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?107375</url></doc>
